Package: cat.survey
Title: Survey Response Classification with LLMs
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Chris", "Soria", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "chris.soria@nyu.edu")
Description: R interface to the Python cat-survey package. Classifies, extracts,
    and explores open-ended survey responses using LLMs. A thin domain wrapper
    around cat.stack that adds the survey_question parameter for survey-specific
    context.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
